title: Frank Lloyd Wright Tree Of Life Metal Bookmark
description:
Frank Lloyd Wright often included stylized designs from nature in his art glass windows, rugs, fabrics, and home furnishings. The Darwin D. Martin House was the most expansive of Wright's prairie-style homes, including several buildings and gardens. Based on a window created for the main house in Buffalo. 
Bookmark is packaged in a recycled PET plastic sleeve with provenance card.

  • Dimensions: 1.25 x 3.25 in.
  • Materials: Solid brass, electro-plated with hematite finish, giclée print
